               <p>On the 15th instant I lost a copper from the wash-house, I live in <placeName id="t17830226-42-crimeloc232">Whitechapel</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17830226-42-crimeloc232" type="placeName" value="Whitechapel"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17830226-42-crimeloc232" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
